data.description: ***New Roof!*** Check out this charming rancher on the Mesa with a circle driveway, covered front porch, and inviting curb appeal. Well water inside and out removes that pesky water bill! Surrounded by farmland, but less than 10-minute drive to downtown Pueblo - it's country living with all the benefits of the city!  Great natural lighting gives warmth and shine to the beautiful hardwood floors. Split floorplan with separate master suite.  Open kitchen - dining room - living room area, perfect for entertaining.  Extensive counter space, modern stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, pantry closet, and extra bar-seating.  Master suite has a walk-in closet and walk-in shower, and enough room to accommodate a sitting area next to full-size bed.  At the other end are 2 large bedrooms each with closets, just down from the large, full bathroom. Separate laundry room. Back patio off of the kitchen is perfect for grilling.  Oversized detached 1-car garage with room for storage / work area on the side.  Fenced dog-run. Room for RV storage, boats and other outdoor hobbies / toys.  1/4 mi to South Mesa Elementary School.
